title.rendered: NFT Fashion at MVMF international festival 29-31 October

content.rendered:
The World's first International Metaverse Music Festival is happening in multiple Metaverses and in the Multiverse during the weekend of October 29, 30, 31. It unites musicians and art lovers, tech guys and philosophers from all around the globe and will showcase many unique artists. Multiverse stage of MVMF, organized by Gleb Divov with support from the Pepinieres, Transculture, Artcomtec, FAYR Ecosystem and 24Fashion.tv will include music performances, art, fashion and panel discussions.

One of the focuses of the MVMF is a growing industry of VR wearables. 24Fashion.tv is supporting artists and fashion designers who create digital clothes with future NFT innovations. Don't miss our interviews with the fashion leaders of the future. The festival will have additional sessions on 12 and 13 November in the Republic of Uupis, Vilnius, Lithuania in the context of Uupis' Vjo dienos festival featuring exclusive live performance of the "Paradise Now" and a special No Lockdown Video selection. Find additional information in the official MVMF twitter Official MVMF website. Explore more about the latest in NFT innovations at FAYR
